text:
I recently read a thread about young women in academia & what they should wear to be professional.

Why, oh why, were the proposed solutions:
- don't wear colorful clothing
- don't wear "too much" makeup
- don't wear "flashy" jewelry

My advice: Don't dull your shine for ANYONE.
